Description:
No other choice but to lock in 😣📚

#collegelife #finals #atubusiness #arkansastech

A big thank you to Academy Sports + Outdoors for allowing our Principles of Marketing class to take over your store on Thursday for our class!! We got to learn all about what it takes to run one of these retail locations! And take a look at some of the pictures from our scavenger hunt, where we were asked to find different marketing tactics that were being used throughout the store!
A couple days ago we wrapped up the semester with a great nuclear bingo event! Congrats to our winners and thank you to everyone who showed up.

Account name: ATU LeMoyne Smith School of Business
Description: Our students absolutely went feral at the Business Bucks auction today 😭💰 Congrats to the winners!

International Week was absolutely unforgettable! 🌍  From cultural performances and global food, flags and so many fun events throughout the week. 💫
As an international student, I am so proud to represent my country on campus and share my culture with others. ❤️
I loved meeting new people, learning about different traditions, and seeing our campus come together as one global family.

FIRST-GEN WEEK RECAP! 🪩

Campus Life and the First-Gen Org made this my favorite first-gen week yet. After an early-morning kickoff, riveting game night, relaxing spa day, entertaining diy night, delicious luncheon, iconic Green and Gold Giveback, AND a super cool block party, I am worn out! 

I am so happy I got to spend the week celebrating our uniqueness and sharing our stories with friends and colleagues. 💚💛 #firstgen #firstgenweek

Night One at Tucker was a hit! Basketball season starts this Friday and I couldn’t be more excited for our Wonder Boys and Golden Suns!
#atubusiness #atuathletics #goarkansastech
Fall Fest 2025 was such a success! 🍁 Grateful for good vibes, pumpkins and so much fun 💫🎃

Another year of Green and Gold Giveback complete! Us Good As Gold Ambassadors spent our Saturday morning giving back to our community by raking leaves, painting, organizing, and helping different businesses, organizations, and community members. 🍂🍁

Description:
Some legacies don’t fade, they lead the way.

Before the bright lights of the @nfl, there was Russellville, Arkansas. Before the roar of the crowd, there was a Wonder Boy who played for something bigger than himself.

Eddie Meador didn’t chase fame, he built it through heart, humility, and hard work that still echo through @arkansastech today.

He became a record-breaking @rams player. A leader. A legend.

And as today’s Wonder Boys pull on that same number, they don’t just wear his legacy, they carry it forward. @atuathletics 

🏈 It’s time for Eddie Meador’s name to live where it belongs… in the Pro Football Hall of Fame. @profootballhof

Canton, Ohio 44708-2699
